11
00:02:13,920 --> 00:02:18,830
to the revive of homeopathic knowledge and for his tireless efforts in training homeopaths

12
00:02:18,930 --> 00:02:24,330
to the highest standards so Homeopathy can claim a place in science as an effective

13
00:02:24,430 --> 00:02:28,570
alternative to other Medical Schools and traditions.

14
00:02:28,670 --> 00:02:31,560
As Director of the Athenian School of homeopathic Medicine,

15
00:02:31,660 --> 00:02:35,810
George Vithoulkas has a team of 30 doctors who practice Homeopathy

16
00:02:35,910 --> 00:02:38,560
while they study under his supervision.

17
00:02:38,660 --> 00:02:42,990
He has established Homeopathy in Greece as a science respected by the medical profession

18
00:02:43,090 --> 00:02:49,490
and made his country one of the leading centers for Homeopathy in the western world.

19
00:02:49,590 --> 00:02:53,980
